{"body": "I don't see the value to still have the `update_column` since we are adding a method that can be used to one or more fields.\n\nThat said I proposing the following path:\n\n* `update_attributes` - hit validations, hit callbacks, respect mass assignment\n* `update_columns` - ignore validations, ignore callbacks, ignore mass assignment\n\n`update_attribute` was removed in 4.0 (#6738) and deprecated in 3-2-stable (#6739)\n`update_column` will be deprecated in 4.0 and remove in the next major release.\n\nI'll work on this.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7192028", "created_at": "2012-07-23T21:30:23Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1190#issuecomment-7192028", "updated_at": "2012-07-23T21:30:23Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1190, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52385be6bd3543c151011ea0"}, "id": 7192028, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/